! H1 Path-Finding Projector

H1 maps complex velocity and chirp information into N-space for path tracing.
The mined conversations separate it from M2: H1 is the route projector, while
M2 remains a separate aliasing fix.

!! Why It Matters

Periodic or chirp-like data can be highly compressible but poorly classified if
the discriminant was calibrated before H1 existed.

